IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. MAGNETIC-FLUX-DENSITY.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  PI          PIC 9(4)V99 VALUE 3.1416.
01  B           PIC 9(4)V99.
01  U           PIC 9(4)V99 VALUE 1.0000.
01  I           PIC 9(4)V99 VALUE 1.0000.
01  R           PIC 9(4)V99 VALUE 1.0000.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    COMPUTE B = (U * I) / (2 * PI * R)
    DISPLAY "The magnetic flux density is: " B
    STOP RUN.

